         Help us lead the charge against cancer
        </h2>
        <div class="flex-subhead">
         <em>
          Join us at the UCI Anti-Cancer Challenge on June 8 and help support life-saving cancer research at the UCI Chao Family Comprehensive Cancer Center. Whether you ride, run, walk or volunteer, your participation move us one step closer to finding cures for a disease that touches us all.
