         <img src="http://give.uci.edu/img/home/flexslider/give-960.png"/>
        </a>
        <h2 class="flex-headline">
         Landmark $200 million gift launches major integrative health initiative
        </h2>
        <div class="flex-subhead">
         <em>
          A $200 million donation from Susan and Henry Samueli, longtime campus supporters, will name a first-of-its-kind College of Health Sciences focused on interdisciplinary integrative health. This far-reaching gift positions UCI as a bold, new leader in population health, patient care, education and research.
         </em>
