      <h2 class="bucket-header">
       News
      </h2>
      <a href="https://news.uci.edu/2018/11/27/uci-to-lead-national-study-on-value-of-liberal-arts-education/">
       <img alt="News" src="/recognition/gifts/img/uci-to-lead-national-study-on-value-of-liberal-arts-education-640x410.jpg"/>
      </a>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Foundation-funded project will impact student achievement
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       <em>
        The Andrew W. Mellon Foundation has named UCI the national pilot site for a three-year project that aims to increase our understanding of what makes a liberal arts education so valuable. This project has tremendous potential to impact educational outcomes and student achievement.
       </em>
      </p>
      <p>
