      <p>
       <strong>
        Let your passions live on with a planned gift
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       <em>
        Whether your passions are the arts, athletics, research, healthcare or molding the minds of our future leaders, a planned gift to UCI can help create your legacy while preserving what you love. We are here to help you choose the planned gift that’s right for you.
       </em>
